{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To put the frozen potatoes so you can-- you know, your hands were frozen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Your feet were frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, they were frozen that you were cutting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cut-- you cut-- and it was winter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So there was a guy called-- and that was a horrible job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they had this guy-- a kapo-- going around with a stick and, 'Schnell, schnell,' you know, to-- to work faster and faster and faster.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was just a sadist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he used to beat us on the head and used to-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his name, I-- I haven't forgotten his name and I can still see his face-- his name was Bomba.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Called Bomba, and he was a Spanish guy, a little Spanish fellow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a kapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a kapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was there for, obviously-- for-- for either-- he was a gangster or a criminal or-- well, obviously, he was, because he was this kapo and he had-- he had the right to kill if he wanted to-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was unbearable, because we were being hit all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You stay-- you sit there and you try to cut those frozen potatoes and you're being hit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and there's only bone and skin, because we could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were that thin, you see, from-- there was no food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this-- this little story gave us a bit of courage and, in a way, helped us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all started to cry and pray.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see, the teaching of [HEBREW], when I was a little boy, it paid off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all could-- all of us could pray.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for the first time, we prayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
